{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>ViuTV年度音樂盛事《CHILL CLUB推介榜 年度推介25/26》今晚假亞博舉行，「CHILL CLUB年度男歌手」的金、銀、銅獎分別是姜濤、Anson Lo（盧瀚霆）和</p><p>ViuTV年度音樂盛事《CHILL CLUB推介榜 年度推介25/26》今晚假亞博舉行，「CHILL CLUB年度男歌手」的金、銀、銅獎分別是姜濤、Anson Lo（盧瀚霆）和張天斌（MC）。MC當知道得講感言時銅獎一刻，面色一沉無甚表情，上台只多謝了三個單位：「多謝Chill Club、多謝華納、多謝賦二代。」然後哼笑兩聲「哈哈」，隨後說：「好開心可以上呢個台度各逐男歌手，Thank you」，拋一下咪即急速落台。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127745325407408128892173.jpeg/UzQwx69BDTtAJ2K5qI8QylnLzeuCh2mrudWCebnVgnk\" alt=\"張天斌奪「CHILL CLUB年度男歌手」銅獎。（節目截圖）\"><figcaption>張天斌奪「CHILL CLUB年度男歌手」銅獎。（節目截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127745322936832000731860.jpeg/Ni0XR5AY1vQDnjInsXE2Z8kyi9seGhWHJaABKSWgASk\" alt=\"言簡意賅。（節目截圖）\"><figcaption>言簡意賅。（節目截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127745319811944448645713.jpeg/xbjCxLha8aTC1B6ds74_io3Bs4pFKsaMbv0IN279CDc\" alt=\"火速離去。（節目截圖）\"><figcaption>火速離去。（節目截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127751079220613120073612.jpeg/R3NzosET2NC-B5ZJp56LEG3di-EOcY_tZZg8kl-YPJI\" alt=\"MC只簡單多謝三組人。（陳順禎 攝）\"><figcaption>MC只簡單多謝三組人。（陳順禎 攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127745480613171200967325.jpeg/RY2MyNqMVGL1dU0ni4KnU5PWtlOE_uGsNRTU1jUU1NY\" alt=\"Anson Lo奪銀獎，MC表情耐人尋味。（節目截圖）\"><figcaption>Anson Lo奪銀獎，MC表情耐人尋味。（節目截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127745730719518720760541.jpeg/MBmRTuEikV95j70PAlvrcCpMpQjWWKPZFDHzyhQx88o\" alt=\"Anson Lo奪銀獎。（節目截圖）\"><figcaption>Anson Lo奪銀獎。（節目截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127745735593562112134082.jpeg/zGu6A098AHtyGrQpCuxFttwYl3FWX-3ytjI0bLYyNGw\" alt=\"粉紅海！（節目截圖）\"><figcaption>粉紅海！（節目截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127750017117851648031592.jpeg/kppkc6KBKY8KuQ-bB-COq2MrEFbKIRIKX6QS0mWkEtI\" alt=\"Anson Lo今年輸俾姜濤。（陳順禎 攝）\"><figcaption>Anson Lo今年輸俾姜濤。（陳順禎 攝）</figcaption></figure><p>姜濤奪金獎：一個人教識咗我咩係真正嘅愛</p><p>首度贏Anson Lo奪男歌手金獎的姜濤在台上有感而發：「前幾日啱啱過咗27歲生日，自己覺得如果喺人生入邊揀最難嘅一年，係我26歲嘅呢一年，咁好彩都過咗去啦，而家又大個咗一歲27歲啦，我心入邊好想多謝一個人，係佢教識咗我咩係真正嘅愛，教識咗我點樣變成一個更加好嘅人，所以相信27歲嘅姜濤嚟緊一定會比以前嘅任何一年更加好，多謝大家。」</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127745733261398016346508.jpeg/t2uUNA8kwaacHbQi7U7WHDWhSmqguPZRLMbK2CzGytg\" alt=\"姜濤金獎在台上有感而發。（節目截圖）\"><figcaption>姜濤金獎在台上有感而發。（節目截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127749850746589184761240.jpeg/EolTRCFCtwfWEhDl5a7NvMNngBBwwBQ6F-6iXy3uol8\" alt=\"（陳順禎 攝）\"><figcaption>（陳順禎 攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-03T15:40:42.762830+00:00","quality":{"score":2,"chars":668,"images":10,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}